    "body": "Another issue on the same packet :\r\n\r\n[According to the devp2p specs](https://github.com/ethereum/devp2p/blob/master/rlpx.md#initial-handshake) : \"Implementations must also ignore any additional list elements in auth-body and ack-body.\"  if a node send a rlpx ping with extra data fields in auth-body node should ignore this.\r\n\r\nIf i send a ping packet with two additional fields who contains the string 59>32#;:9%(0<?9:@\"/ ,Erigon don't respond and i get an EOF.",
